:attr:`icalendar.prop.binary.vBinary.obj` is deprecated in favour of :attr:`~icalendar.prop.binary.vBinary.bytes`. It is retained as a (lossy) string view of the value for backward compatibility and will be removed in icalendar 8. The ``test_ical_value_rejects_non_base64_characters`` test was removed because ``ical_value`` no longer validates or decodes base64. @uwezkhan
